'''加拿大聯盟'''（{{lang-en|'''Canadian Alliance'''}}；{{lang-fr|'''Alliance canadienne'''}}），正式名稱爲'''加拿大改革保守聯盟'''（{{lang-en|'''Canadian Reform Conservative Alliance'''}}；{{lang-fr|'''Alliance réformiste-conservatrice canadienne'''}}）是一個存在於2000年至2003年的[[保守主義|保守主義]]和[[右翼民粹主義|右翼民粹主義]]政黨，它是[[加拿大改革黨|加拿大改革黨]]的繼承者，在其存在時間內一直是[[加拿大國會下議院|下議院]]的[[官方反對黨_(加拿大)|官方反對黨]]。該政黨支持[[財政保守主義|財政保守主義]]和[[社會保守主義|社會保守主義]]的政策，並尋求降低政府對社會項目的支出及扣減稅項。

該黨在2003年12月與[[加拿大進步保守黨|進步保守黨]]合併爲[[加拿大保守黨|加拿大保守黨]]。

== 歷史 ==
=== 改革黨起源 ===
加拿大聯盟的前身為於1987年成立的[[加拿大改革黨|加拿大改革黨]]。1980年代初中期，在[[魁北克主权运动|魁北克主權問題]]和修憲協議主宰聯邦政壇的局面下，[[加拿大西部|加拿大西部]]的選民感到被忽略<ref name="CECon">{{cite web |title=Conservative Party |url=http://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.ca/en/article/conservative-party/ |publisher=The Canadian Encyclopedia |accessdate=2016-03-02 |archive-date=2018-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180109190710/http://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.ca/en/article/conservative-party/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。為了在聯邦層面反映當地訴求，一群加西地區組織於1986年組建聯盟，並於1987年通過組成改革黨，由曼寧（{{lang|en|Preston Manning}}）出任黨魁<ref name="CEReform">{{cite web |title=Reform Party of Canada |url=http://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.ca/en/article/reform-party-of-canada/ |publisher=The Canadian Encyclopedia |accessdate=2017-08-16 |first=Trevor W. |last=Harrison |date=2006-02-07 |archive-date=2017-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170802054838/http://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.ca/en/article/reform-party-of-canada/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。改革黨提倡在加拿大政治制度中增強[[直接民主|直接民主]]元素（如舉行[[公民投票|公民投票]]和[[罷免選舉|罷免選舉]]）、更改[[加拿大上議院|加拿大上議院]]議員的產生辦法（從委任制改為由民選產生，並增加代表加西地區的議席）、以及減低聯邦政府的規模和開支<ref name="CEReform"/>。此外，該黨亦有不少黨員和支持者為社會保守主義者。

當時在聯邦層面執政的[[加拿大進步保守黨|進步保守黨]]除了流失加西選民支持外，修憲失敗亦導致[[魁北克|魁北克]]民族主義支持者轉投[[魁人政團|魁人政團]]<ref name="CECon"/>，而經濟低迷引致失業率高企，加上[[馬丁·布賴恩·馬爾羅尼|馬爾羅尼]]政府於1991年開徵[[加拿大銷售稅|貨勞稅]]，令進步保守黨的民望進一步下跌<ref name="LAC">{{cite web | url=http://www.bac-lac.gc.ca/eng/discover/politics-government/prime-ministers/pmportrait/pages/item.aspx?PersonId=19 | publisher=Library and Archives Canada | title=A. Kim Campbell - Canada's 19th Prime Minister | accessdate=2016-02-21 | date=2014-06-03 | archive-date=2016-10-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161002083756/http://www.bac-lac.gc.ca/eng/discover/politics-government/prime-ministers/pmportrait/pages/item.aspx?PersonId=19 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，並讓改革黨有機可乘。改革黨先於1989年透過格雷（{{lang|en|Deborah Grey}}）贏取[[愛民頓|愛民頓]]選區議席補選首進[[加拿大國會下議院|下議院]]，再於1993年聯邦大選贏取52席（除了一席位於[[安大略省|安大略省]]外其餘全位於加西），取代僅餘兩席的進步保守黨成為下議院内的主要右翼政黨<ref name="CECon"/><ref name="CEReform"/>。

改革黨於1997年聯邦大選首次成為[[官方反對黨_(加拿大)|官方反對黨]]，但未能擴闊票源，所贏取的60個議席全數代表加西地區<ref name="CEReform"/>。進步保守黨在該屆大選表現略有改善，議席數目上升至20席<ref name="CECon"/>。面對當時加拿大右翼選票被改革黨和進步保守黨攤分的局面，曼寧成立「聯合替代」運動（{{lang|en|United Alternative}}）以尋求結合兩黨並挑戰[[加拿大自由黨|聯邦自由黨]]的執政地位。然而，包括黨魁[[查爾斯·約瑟夫·克拉克|克拉克]]在內的進步保守黨高層拒絕與改革黨合作，兩黨合併遂並未成事<ref name="CBCarchives02">{{cite news | url=http://www.cbc.ca/archives/entry/uneasy-alliance | work=CBC News | title=Uneasy alliance - CBC Digital Archives | accessdate=2016-03-04 | archive-date=2016-03-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160311080010/http://www.cbc.ca/archives/entry/uneasy-alliance | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 加拿大聯盟成立 ===
[[File:Vladimir_Putin_in_Canada_18-19_December_2000-11.jpg|thumb]]與[[俄羅斯總統|俄羅斯總統]][[普京|普京]]會面（攝於2000年12月）]]

改革黨於2000年初在[[渥太華|渥太華]]舉行兩場「聯合替代」全國大會<ref name="CEReform"/>，黨員於第二場大會中表決是否尋求與進步保守黨建立合作關係，該項建議獲60.5%選票通過<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manning-gets-approval-for-united-alternative-1.189897 |title=Manning gets approval for United Alternative |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2017-08-16 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/manning-gets-approval-for-united-alternative-1.189897 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。改革黨遂告解散，並由新成立的'''加拿大改革保守聯盟'''取代<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-party-changes-embarrassing-acronym-1.240933 |title=New party changes embarrassing acronym |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2017-08-16 |date=2000-02-02 |archive-date=2017-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171021130605/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-party-changes-embarrassing-acronym-1.240933 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，政綱包括將所有國民的[[入息税|入息税率]][[單一税|劃一]]為17%和強制聯邦政府平衡預算<ref name="CEAlliance">{{cite web |title=Canadian Alliance |url=http://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.ca/en/article/canadian-alliance/ |publisher=The Canadian Encyclopedia |accessdate=2017-08-17 |first=Trevor W. |last=Harrison |date=2006-02-07 |archive-date=2017-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170820165437/http://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.ca/en/article/canadian-alliance/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。進步保守黨黨魁克拉克繼續抨擊加拿大聯盟<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/clark-calls-canadian-alliance-manipulative-1.211930 |title=Clark calls Canadian Alliance "manipulative" |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2017-08-16 |date=2000-04-04 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/clark-calls-canadian-alliance-manipulative-1.211930 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但兩黨結合的建議則獲包括[[安大略進步保守黨|安大略進步保守黨]]籍內閣部長甘禮明（{{lang|en|Tony Clement}}）在內的數名省級保守派人士支持<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/united-alternative-showdown-set-to-begin-1.212645 |title=United Alternative showdown set to begin |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2017-08-16 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/united-alternative-showdown-set-to-begin-1.212645 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

加拿大聯盟黨魁選舉首輪投票於2000年6月24日舉行，[[亞伯達|亞伯達]][[亞伯達省議會|省議員]]及該省財政部長[[戴國衛|戴國衛]]贏取44%選票排行第一，與得票第二高的曼寧雙雙出線<ref name="CBC000624">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/day-manning-win-first-alliance-leadership-vote-1.212433 |title=Day, Manning win first Alliance leadership vote |publisher=CBC News |date=2000-06-24 |accessdate=2017-08-12 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/day-manning-win-first-alliance-leadership-vote-1.212433 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在同年7月8日舉行的次輪投票中，戴國衛以63.4%得票率壓倒曼寧，當選加拿大聯盟黨魁<ref name="CBC000709">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-day-for-canadian-alliance-1.248371 |title=New Day for Canadian Alliance |publisher=CBC News |date=2000-07-09 |accessdate=2017-08-12 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-day-for-canadian-alliance-1.248371 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。戴國衛隨後辭去亞伯達省議員職務，並於同年9月11日贏取[[卑詩省|卑詩省]]奧卡拿根－高貴哈拉選區國會議席補選，從而晉身下議院<ref name="CBC000912">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/stockwell-s-day-1.222849 |title=Stockwell's day |publisher=CBC News |date=2000-09-12 |accessdate=2017-08-12 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/stockwell-s-day-1.222849 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

自由黨籍[[加拿大總理|總理]][[讓·克雷蒂安|克雷蒂安]]於數星期後宣布將下屆聯邦大選提早至2000年11月27日舉行<ref name="CBC001023">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/mps-start-campaigning-before-pm-calls-election-1.238670 |title=MPs start campaigning before PM calls election |publisher=CBC News |date=2000-10-23 |accessdate=2017-08-13 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/mps-start-campaigning-before-pm-calls-election-1.238670 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；外界認為此舉是為了縮短加拿大聯盟準備競選活動的時間<ref name="CBC000925">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/will-pm-call-fall-election-1.213225 |title=Will PM call fall election? |publisher=CBC News |date=2000-09-25 |accessdate=2017-08-13 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/will-pm-call-fall-election-1.213225 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。儘管如此，加拿大聯盟中人期望在戴國衛領導下能在[[安大略省|安大略省]]取得突破，並對大選結果審慎樂觀。民意調查顯示加拿大聯盟的支持度從10月中的19%上升至10月末的28%，分析指該股氣勢若持續下去的話，自由黨可能失去多數黨地位，加拿大聯盟更有些微機會掌政<ref name="CBC001030">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/cbc-poll-suggests-liberals-in-lead-alliance-surge-1.247468 |title=CBC poll suggests Liberals in lead, Alliance surge |publisher=CBC News |date=2000-10-30 |accessdate=2017-08-13 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/cbc-poll-suggests-liberals-in-lead-alliance-surge-1.247468 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。加拿大聯盟終在這次大選贏取66席，全國得票率約為26%，延續改革黨的官方反對黨地位<ref name="CEAlliance"/>。該黨在加西表現理想，分別取得卑詩省34席中的27席和亞伯達省26席中的23席。然而，該黨只在安大略省103席中贏取兩席，未能擺脫自由黨操控安省的局面<ref name="CBC001129">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/the-day-after-the-night-before-1.199736 |title=The day after the night before |publisher=CBC News |date=2000-11-29 |accessdate=2017-08-13 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/the-day-after-the-night-before-1.199736 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

聯盟在安省表現欠佳，加上戴國衛受數項不利消息困擾，導致部分黨員開始質疑他的領導能力。包括副黨魁格雷和下議院官方反對黨首席議員施察奧（{{lang|en|Chuck Strahl}}）在内的數名黨內高層於2001年4月末辭去[[影子內閣|影子內閣]]職務，但戴國衛堅持留任黨魁<ref name="CBC010425">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/day-fends-off-leadership-questions-as-key-caucus-members-resign-1.261199 |title=Day fends off leadership questions as key caucus members resign |publisher=CBC News |date=2001-04-25 |accessdate=2017-08-14 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/day-fends-off-leadership-questions-as-key-caucus-members-resign-1.261199 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；格雷和施察奧等人於往後數月內自行離開或被逐出黨團<ref name="CBC010515">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/dissident-mps-ready-to-break-from-day-s-leadership-1.273937 |title=Dissident MPs ready to break from Day's leadership |publisher=CBC News |date=2001-05-15 |accessdate=2017-08-14 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/dissident-mps-ready-to-break-from-day-s-leadership-1.273937 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。面對黨內鬥爭，戴國衛於7月中宣布提早舉行黨魁選舉<ref name="CBC010718">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/alliance-prepares-for-leadership-race-1.280078 |title=Alliance prepares for leadership race |publisher=CBC News |date=2001-07-18 |accessdate=2017-08-14 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/alliance-prepares-for-leadership-race-1.280078 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另一方面，格雷、施察奧和另外十名黨員則於同期籌組成「民主代表黨團」（{{lang|en|Democratic Representative Caucus}}）<ref name="CBC010719">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/alliance-dissidents-to-form-democractic-representative-caucus-1.278010 |title=Alliance dissidents to form 'Democractic Representative Caucus' |publisher=CBC News |date=2001-07-19 |accessdate=2017-08-14 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/alliance-dissidents-to-form-democractic-representative-caucus-1.278010 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於8月中與進步保守黨高層會面，商討在國會內加強合作<ref name="CBC010817">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/alliance-leadership-vote-set-for-march-1.281598 |title=Alliance leadership vote set for March |publisher=CBC News |date=2001-08-17 |accessdate=2017-08-14 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/alliance-leadership-vote-set-for-march-1.281598 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。黨魁選舉首輪投票結果於2002年3月20日公布，[[史蒂芬·哈珀|哈珀]]贏取過半數選票擊敗戴國衛和另外兩位候選人當選黨魁<ref name="CBC020320">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/harper-wins-alliance-leadership-1.322969 |title=Harper wins Alliance leadership |publisher=CBC News |date=2002-03-20 |accessdate=2017-08-14 |archive-date=2018-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180509112521/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/harper-wins-alliance-leadership-1.322969 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。除了兩名下議院議員外，大部分民主代表黨團成員皆於哈珀當選黨魁後重返聯盟黨團。

=== 邁向合併 ===
克拉克未能重建進步保守黨在國内的廣泛支持<ref name="CECon"/>，並於2002年8月宣佈辭任黨魁<ref name="CBCindepth01">{{cite news | url=http://www.cbc.ca/news2/background/conservativeparty/pcparty.html | work=CBC News | title=The PC Party | date=2005-05-03 | accessdate=2016-03-04 | archive-date=2016-03-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305153354/http://www.cbc.ca/news2/background/conservativeparty/pcparty.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[彼得·麥凱|-{zh-hans:彼得·麦凯;zh-hk:彼得·馬逵;zh-tw:彼得·麥凱;}-]]於2003年5月31日當選新任進步保守黨黨魁，該黨和加拿大聯盟高層在往後數個月内就合併事宜磋商<ref name="CBC031009">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/alliance-pc-merger-talks-reach-critical-point-1.366247 |title=Alliance, PC merger talks reach critical point |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2003-10-09 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305225136/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/alliance-pc-merger-talks-reach-critical-point-1.366247 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。哈珀和麥凱於同年10月16日共同宣佈達成協議，將兩黨合併成新的[[加拿大保守黨|加拿大保守黨]]<ref name="CBC031016">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/harper-and-mackay-announce-deal-to-unite-the-right-1.391784 |title=Harper and MacKay announce deal to unite the right |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2003-10-16 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305153348/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/harper-and-mackay-announce-deal-to-unite-the-right-1.391784 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這項合併於同年12月5日獲95.9%的加拿大聯盟代表投票支持<ref name="CBC031205">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/alliance-members-vote-95-9-in-favour-of-merger-1.397973 |title=Alliance members vote 95.9% in favour of merger |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2017-08-17 |date=2003-12-05 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126083015/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/alliance-members-vote-95-9-in-favour-of-merger-1.397973 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而加拿大保守黨亦於同月8日正式登記成立<ref name="CBC031216">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/conservative-party-unveils-new-logo-1.406118 |title=Conservative party unveils new logo |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2003-12-16 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305153351/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/conservative-party-unveils-new-logo-1.406118 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，加拿大聯盟遂告終結。

